5.3 DUIM-Sheets Module

port?

Generic function

Summary

Returns true if the specified object is a port.

Signature

Arguments

object
An instance of type <object>.

Values

boolean
An instance of type <boolean>.

Library

duim-sheets

Module

duim-sheets

Description
